  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Uprising frames another sweep through modern Necromunda around Caleb Cursebound and a wider set of downhive rebellions, escapes and terrible bargains. Yar Umbra cuts a path through Hive Primus seeking a way off Necromunda; a House Cawdor juve finds a statue of the Emperor that can remake his life; a Corpse Guild drudge learns why some secrets must stay buried; and Caleb runs for Hope's End with enemies on his reputation as much as his heels. A multi-author anthology of hive unrest, faith, hunger and little revolutions, where the Underhive keeps turning private desperation into public violence and nobody leaves clean.",
